{"tid":1640272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【左膠connect】希拉莉：每位美國人都有權發聲支持香港民主及人權","createTime":"2019-10-09T01:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T08:08:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"38b90cffb653b8198a2242b596381d507381fa97","tid":1640272,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:52:12.000Z","msg":"NBA休斯敦火箭隊總經理莫雷（Daryl Morey）支持香港示威言論引來各方激烈回應，央視及騰訊（00700）紛即時暫停NBA季前賽（中國賽）的轉播安排，多家中資贊助商都中止與火箭的合作。不過，莫雷卻得到美國前國務卿希拉莉（Hillary Clinton）的力撐。<br />\n<br />\n希拉莉周二在Twitter表示，每位美國人都有權發聲支持香港的民主及人權。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2465000/2467987/hillary-tw_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2465000%2F2467987%2Fhillary-tw_1024.jpg&h=c5cf5880&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希拉莉的言論相信與火箭總經理莫雷（Daryl Morey）早前表態撐港風波風波有關。莫雷在Twitter聲援香港示威者，引來中方不滿，群起封殺。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2467987/%E3%80%90NBA%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%E3%80%91%E5%B8%8C%E6%8B%89%E8%8E%89%EF%BC%9A%E6%AF%8F%E4%BD%8D%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E6%AC%8A%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E5%8F%8A%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A?mtc=20023</code></pre>"},{"pid":"c9037a4f4d00bdf5ae5b00b2ddf26427f0a3410a","tid":1640272,"uid":18074,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:53:40.000Z","msg":"美國左膠先最支持民主"},{"pid":"68c78096250c98e91f8addbd033de951cb6427ab","tid":1640272,"uid":176996,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:54:59.000Z","msg":"Connet"},{"pid":"9aab461149259e1a532e27886313855764f101e5","tid":1640272,"uid":136987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:55:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57cbcffae0dfe8a44e9ad0ca57802676b02cfe66","tid":1640272,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-